{"tid":1220710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中西區樂悠遊（交通攻略）","createTime":"2019-06-14T05:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T05:24:14.000Z","uid":23390,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4822b2b2926486bcbb23eae71b215a7ac5a81505","tid":1220710,"uid":23390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:09:33.000Z","msg":"六月尾，一班學生又放暑假，條假又多咗好多人。放假未必一定要去銅鑼灣／旺角／尖沙咀呢啲購物區，港島地區好似灣仔／中環／金鐘都有好多地方比你放鬆休息下。上至五星級酒店Conrad/ Shangrila，下至免費香港公園／大會堂／展城遊覽，一定啱啱哂唔同年齡層嘅人參考。<br />\n<br />\n首先介紹交通，宜家地鐵越加越貴，一個唔覺意又岀事故，唔通留係九龍新界浪費自己個假期咩！加上紅隊過海咁平，又成日塞車，今次介紹下如果由九龍前往港島，有啲咩方法最啱你！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">旺角</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>1. 紅van </ins></span></span><br />\n【旺角金雞廣場至香港仔華富村】<br />\n呢架紅van過咗西隧就係西營盤（岀咗隧道第一個紅綠燈口位後嗌有落 ~高樂花園），你可以選擇轉搭叮叮呢款只係港島擁有嘅交通工具，享受下慢活人生（於干諾道中落車後背向海邊行，到達德輔道西就見到電車路）。搵電車路好易，只要留意地下電車路軌及電線桿，只要唔搭錯方向就可以。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">電車實時到站及路線<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hktramways.com/tc/interactive-map\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hktramways.com%2Ftc%2Finteractive-map&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=18185778\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hktramways.com/tc/interactive-map</a></span><br />\n<br />\n【旺角弼街始創中心至港鐵堅尼地城站】<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"http://www.16seats.net/chi/rmb/r_kh04.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.16seats.net%2Fchi%2Frmb%2Fr_kh04.html&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=f2f2740a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.16seats.net/chi/rmb/r_kh04.html</a></span><br />\n呢條路線都係行西隧，過咗西隧搵到電車搭就可以。<br />\n<br />\n【旺角招商永隆銀行中心至西環】<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"http://www.16seats.net/chi/rmb/r_kh21.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.16seats.net%2Fchi%2Frmb%2Fr_kh21.html&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=b1c61d44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.16seats.net/chi/rmb/r_kh21.html</a></span><br />\n呢架行紅隧，有機會因交通阻塞令交通時間受影響。過咗紅隧到銅鑼灣後，可以於分域街／金鐘道／德己立街下車步行前往目的地。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">其他紅van路線可參考各區紅van小巴薈<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.16seats.net/chi/rmb/r_wcc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.16seats.net%2Fchi%2Frmb%2Fr_wcc.html&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=c9f3c18d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.16seats.net/chi/rmb/r_wcc.html</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">紅van好處：</span></strong><br />\n   -只要你落得快，司機咩位都可以比你落<br />\n   -車程短，絕對唔會塞車（除非交通意外），旺角至西營盤只須10分鐘<br />\n   -比其他只識用google map同搭地鐵嘅人多好多交通選擇<br />\n   -基本上你個區有紅van去港島，都可以再轉電車去目的地<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">壞處</span></strong><br />\n   -唔敢嗌落車嘅毒撚幫你唔到<br />\n   -冇時間表，等車時間有可能超過30分鐘至1小時不等<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 旺角巴士</span></span></strong></ins></strong><br />\n如果係旺角搭巴士，大家都可以選擇係彌敦道上車（<span style=\"color: blue;\">地鐵站E2岀口</span>後往大馬路行係往過海方向，岀E1係往九龍方向）。另外如果驚紅隧塞車，可以避免搭三位數巴士（以&rdquo;1&rdquo;開頭的），如112/106，呢啲都係經紅隧過海的。<br />\n如果搭970x/ 971過西隧後，都可以轉搭叮叮前往港島其他地方。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">可善用新巴城巴實時到站app<br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/xin-ba-cheng-ba-citybusnwfb/id472242340\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fxin-ba-cheng-ba-citybusnwfb%2Fid472242340&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=b4f4272b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/xin-ba-cheng-ba-citybusnwfb/id472242340</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nwfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.nwfb&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=a89df504\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nwfb</a><br />\n<br />\n九巴實時到站app<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/app-1933-kmb-lwb/id1170003707?l=zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fapp-1933-kmb-lwb%2Fid1170003707%3Fl%3Dzh&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=ce0e160c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/app-1933-kmb-lwb/id1170003707?l=zh</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kmb.app1933\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.kmb.app1933&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=a6fe7caf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kmb.app1933</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">尖沙咀</span></span></ins></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n【尖沙咀至中環】<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"http://www.starferry.com.hk/tc/service\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.starferry.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fservice&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=e1ae7005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.starferry.com.hk/tc/service</a></span><br />\n最方便方法當然係係尖沙咀碼頭搭去中環，中環落船後可以上天橋前往ifc方向。如果你鍾意行公園海滂嘅，可以往aia海傍空地前進，往金鐘方向行可前往大會堂／展城館等位置。<br />\n<br />\n【尖沙咀至灣仔】<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"http://www.starferry.com.hk/tc/service\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.starferry.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fservice&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=e1ae7005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.starferry.com.hk/tc/service</a></span><br />\n如果你放假繁忙時間見到好多人過海去中環，其實你可以選擇去灣仔先嘅。灣仔碼頭附近有小量巴士搭，你怕熱嘅可以先往會展行，上到天橋往入境處再往灣仔地鐵站行。前往金鐘嘅可以步行前往軒尼詩道。<br />\n<br />\n呢到只係有少量交通攻略，其實仲有好多地方等住大家去發掘，例如係半山區堅尼地道至香港公園<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（重要）</span></strong>，大家得閒無事可以打開google map睇下，好似去旅行咁plan下行程，咁就唔洗放假岀到嚟仲要臨時臨急係街search路線啦。"},{"pid":"2f1b1b3ca6632310475979bfabe0a0a29efaf27b","tid":1220710,"uid":23390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:12:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f183aceb630ecdd157924190e13175a7d96c3f3","tid":1220710,"uid":23390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:12:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7cc3a170765ccff21b9f356f20405afc520bf64e","tid":1220710,"uid":23390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:13:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"606dab66f5ce4a4e847bd1e3b6481e7d36cc005a","tid":1220710,"uid":23390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:13:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7d9c9c5f1308b9d33316b2bbd667e57a6a748cff","tid":1220710,"uid":23390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:13:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2eab9c19ccf71c3da4b3d9d2854256b86647a410","tid":1220710,"uid":23390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:13:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"018ad1d2e500d5388a8716b5a97bd86cc59d56d4","tid":1220710,"uid":23390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:13:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9634c90966462b6e0603bc459b690d9812d052bc","tid":1220710,"uid":23390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:14:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b610ce84ff20c258711851c8ab12560b79f53812","tid":1220710,"uid":23390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:14:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8a0cfef4584e2b60713ed19f05133376d748cf7a","tid":1220710,"uid":23390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:14:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5358ce78ca65aca65761abc6e1421163c2e54df6","tid":1220710,"uid":23390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:15:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"91e71bf5b50a6fbc7227f4072314f456c8ec7161","tid":1220710,"